 *   - finalVars:       names declared with "final" in the current method scope
 *   - initializedVars: names that have been assigned / are params / are finals
 *                      (finals are initialized at declaration)
 *   - localVars:       names declared with SimpleVarDeclaration inside a method
 *                      (these start uninitialized)
 *   - inMethodScope:   true while inside a MethodDeclaration body
